    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the S54 3.2L atmospheric inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, providing direct mechanical linkage and precise gate engagement. The chassis has been addressed for longevity, including rear subframe reinforcement and a recent cooling system refresh. The M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential provides excellent torque distribution out of corners. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition with consistent compression across all cylinders. A true driver\u2019s car for the purist seeking telepathic steering rack feedback and a high-redline visceral experience.",
