      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior paint still holds a high gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches near the trunk\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats show only light bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All interior electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has a documented service history, with a recent oil change and a multi-point inspection performed last month. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, comfortable ride. This is a solid, dependable vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
